Version 4.3.0
Ajout du réseau Lille avec les mêmes stratégies que pour le réseau Bologna. Toutes les intersections n'ont pas été équipées de capteurs.

Version 4.3.2
Retiré un print Le TraciWrapper mesure le temps moyen de toutes les phases du réseau (une seule valeur retournée)

Le TraciWrapper est capable de créer une visualisation sous forme de graphe du réseau avec des couleurs pour indiquer si les voies sont vertes, rouges ou jaunes. N'est réellement efficace que pour les réseaux artificiels.

Version 5.0 : - All the systems have the same strategies classes. - TLS_DETECTORS and TL_IDS have been added to artificial preset networks - Deletion of agents package - RL1 and RL2 systems deleted - Intellilight strategy has been implemented - The TraciWrapper prints the time step of the simulation every print_timestep

Version 5.0 : - All the systems have the same strategies classes. - TLS_DETECTORS and TL_IDS have been added to artificial preset networks - Deletion of agents package - RL1 and RL2 systems deleted - Intellilight strategy has been implemented - The TraciWrapper prints the time step of the simulation every print_timestep

Version 5.0 : - All the systems have the same strategies classes. - TLS_DETECTORS and TL_IDS have been added to artificial preset networks - Deletion of agents package - RL1 and RL2 systems deleted - Intellilight strategy has been implemented - The TraciWrapper prints the time step of the simulation every print_timestep

Version 5.0 : - All the systems have the same strategies classes. - TLS_DETECTORS and TL_IDS have been added to artificial preset networks - Deletion of agents package - RL1 and RL2 systems deleted - Intellilight strategy has been implemented - The TraciWrapper prints the time step of the simulation every print_timestep
- Corrected time-to-teleport. It is now choosable by the user.

- Corrected an issue with Intellilight strategy (number of NN was fixed to 3) - Standardized the way of launching simulations for every network. Simulations are now launched with network objects. All the parameters have to be given to the network object. The Experiment class is obsolete. - The clean_files function is now included into he run function of every run function. You don't need to call it every time tou launch a simulation.
- Corrected parameters in run function for real networks
- Added references to all the strategies
- Added a parameter to traciWrapper to give a list of timesteps when all vehicles in simulation are deleted
- Completed documentation of public functions

- All parameters of the strategies can now be given as an int or a dict. If int, all the intersections have the same value. if dict, intersections take the value stored in the dict. The dict must contain a value for each intersection.

- All parameters of the strategies can now be given as an int or a dict. If int, all the intersections have the same value. if dict, intersections take the value stored in the dict. The dict must contain a value for each intersection. - Changed the name of some parameters of the classes, to delete useless "s"
- Fixed yellow_time bug
- Modified pyproject
- Fixed Intellilight : Episode duration is now set in parameter, and expressed in timestep
- Fixed Intellilight : state and next_state in replay_buffer were the same. Not anymore

- Fixed Intellilight : The system is now almost the same than in the article. The only difference is that we don't use the trhoughput of the intersection in the reward computation. - Acolight has now a supervisor parameter. When desactivated, agents do not cooperate.
- Fixed bugs of coordination for AcoLight - Fixed comparison error in Grid Network - Added functions to get the waiting time of all vehicles in sim
- Can now choose the number of lanes on the LineNetwork
- Added exit detectors on Grid and Line networks - Added multilanes generation on LineNetwork - Corrected the absence of MADDPG in __init__.py

- Corrected ProgramLogics in Bologna that caused errors with most strategies - Corrected self.clearing_time in AnalyticPlus that is now a dict. needed to be called with the ID of the agent. - Disabled the weights_only on RL systems when load_model was called. Torch library changed and it was called by defaults, generating errors.
- Corrected FixedTimeStrategy : Errors of transition
- Added exit detectors to Bologna - Corrected phases of TL 221
- Modified pyproject
- Modified Bologna network : added new numerical detectors to intersection 235 so bus are not ignored for some systems
- Added phase occurences measuring for the strategies that didn't have it
- Corrected non-cyclicity of Max Pressure
- Modified phase times in xml of Bologna
- Strategies now collect the duration of each phases
- Modified pyproject.toml
- Modified phases_durations object : now store a tuple with the phase and its duration, not only the duration
- Added energy consumption measurements with PyRAPL
- Modified a possible bug where behavioural functions could be executed at the same rate than data_frequency - Added a parameter to collect the phase of each TLS at each time step
- Added energy consumption measures
